---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="A bit about Debangan Thakuria — backend engineer, reader, writer, and fish keeper.">
  <article>
    <h1 class="text-3xl mb-8" style="font-family: var(--font-family-heading); font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-text);">
      About
    </h1>

    <div class="prose">
      <p>
        I'm Debangan — a backend software engineer with about four and a half years of experience,
        mostly in distributed systems and API design. I like building things that are simple, correct,
        and boring in the best possible way.
      </p>

      <p>
        I'm also a reader. I grew up on manga and light novels, and somewhere along the way that
        expanded into web novels and the occasional fantasy or sci-fi epic. The stories I gravitate
        towards tend to be long, unhurried, and character-driven — the kind where you spend a hundred
        chapters just learning to care about people.
      </p>

      <p>
        I've been writing my own web novel for a while. Slowly, which is fine. Writing that way feels
        more honest.
      </p>

      <p>
        Outside of that: I go to the gym, I keep fish (currently a betta and a peaceful community
        tank), and I tend to prefer small spaces, quiet evenings, and very good tea.
      </p>

      <p>
        This site is a place to write things I'd otherwise lose to scattered notes. No theme, no
        niche — just whatever's on my mind.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t" style="border-color: var(--color-border);">
      <h2 class="text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-widest mb-6" style="color: var(--color-text-muted);">
        Currently
      </h2>

      <dl class="space-y-4">
        <div>
          <dt class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wide mb-1" style="color: var(--color-text-muted);">Reading</dt>
          <dd class="text-sm" style="color: var(--color-text);">Whatever web novel has pulled me in this week</dd>
        </div>
        <div>
          <dt class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wide mb-1" style="color: var(--color-text-muted);">Watching</dt>
          <dd class="text-sm" style="color: var(--color-text);">Keeping up with the current anime season</dd>
        </div>
        <div>
          <dt class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wide mb-1" style="color: var(--color-text-muted);">Writing</dt>
          <dd class="text-sm" style="color: var(--color-text);">My web novel, slowly and steadily</dd>
        </div>
        <div>
          <dt class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wide mb-1" style="color: var(--color-text-muted);">Working on</dt>
          <dd class="text-sm" style="color: var(--color-text);">Backend infrastructure, distributed systems</dd>
        </div>
      </dl>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
